	 <title>System.ServerName</title> 
	 <para></para> 
	 <bridgehead renderas="sect3">Remarks</bridgehead> 
	 <para>This operator returns the current server name. The server name is
		  specified upon creation. The default server name for both In-Process servers
		  and servers running as a service is "dataphor".</para> 
	 <example> 
		  <title>Example</title> 
		  <programlisting>select TableDee add {ServerName() server };</programlisting> 
		  <programlisting>server   
-------- 
dataphor </programlisting> 
	 </example> 
